    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This device consists of a 1-foot metallic handle fit with a small force generator at one end. As a swift action, you can activate this device and cause it to emit a hardlight pole from the handle that is up to 10 feet long. This pole is solid to the touch but nearly weightless, making it unsuitable as a weapon. You can, however, use it to push things or hang on to it, as it is composed of pure force and virtually indestructible. You can use a hardlight pole for up to an hour per day; each individual use must be in 1-minute increments.</p>"
